  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Data Entry / Admin (Medical Transcriptionist)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<p>We are seeking a Medical Transcriptionist to transcribe doctors' dictations into accurate diagnostic reports, ensure consistency, identify errors, submit records for approval, adhere to confidentiality guidelines, file reports, and perform other assigned duties.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>· Listen to the recorded dictation of doctors.</p>\n<p>· Transcribe and interpret the dictation into diagnotic test results and reports.</p>\n<p>· Make sure the transcription is correct, complete and has a consistent style.</p>\n<p>· Identify inconsistencies, error and missing information within a report that could compromise patient care.</p>\n<p>· Submit health records to physicians for approval.</p>\n<p>· Follow patient confidentiality/guidelines and legal documentation requirements.</p>\n<p>· Filing and upload transcribed reports.</p>\n<p>· Any other duties as assigned by the management.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>· At least Primary/ Secondary School/ 'O' Level, Professional Certificate/ NiTEC, Diploma/ Advanced/ Higher/ Graduate Diploma in any field</p>\n<p>· Related working experience in healthcare and understanding of medical terminology/ abbreviations/ jargon will be added advantage</p>\n<p>· Strong computer skills. Proficient in MS Office Advantage</p>\n<p>· Meticulous, eye for details, precise, organised and efficient</p>\n<p>· Good communication and interpersonal skill</p>\n<p>· Effective team player and able to work in fast paced environment</p>\n<p>· 5.5 days work week (Monday to Friday; Half Saturday)</p>\n<p>· Location: Orchard</p>",
